Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.30,0:00:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在被星光照射的頂屋裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.90,0:00:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,獨自一人聆聽著天空的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.55,0:00:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用玻璃的繃帶遮住眼睛行走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.20,0:00:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家都是孤獨的馬戲團孩子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.85,0:00:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,孤身一人的悲傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.10,0:00:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,震動的繃帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.87,0:00:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,撼動著心靈……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.35,0:01:06.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用溫柔的眼神期待與某人的相會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.05,0:01:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在我耳邊細語「請留在我身邊」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.27,0:01:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Silent Voice
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.54,0:01:34.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二十七話 莉娜的血 上集
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.70,0:02:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉娜小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.30,0:02:13.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起\n這種事交給我來就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.60,0:02:19.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古利明大人會罵我的\n你的手指先不要動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.29,0:02:50.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼會的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.93,0:02:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.30,0:03:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們就是為此降落巴卡魯的\n去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.04,0:03:15.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,白天的時候太勉強了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.53,0:03:17.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說過決勝點在晚上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.82,0:03:22.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迎賓可能會舉辦派對\n我就是要瞄準那時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.14,0:03:26.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再過不久就可以\n吃莉娜好吃的料理了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.15,0:03:27.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾莉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.91,0:03:31.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,救出莉娜之後脫離高達隊好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.64,0:03:33.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.28,0:03:40.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你跟莉娜一起到,別的殖民地生活\n我會寄生活費過去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.03,0:03:41.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那捷度你呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.88,0:03:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要見證這場戰爭到最後\n讓那些任性的大人大吃一驚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.61,0:03:50.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這我知道...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.28,0:03:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此我不希望莉娜在身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.90,0:03:55.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可以留在你身邊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.45,0:04:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露卡他們回來了,午飯也做好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.51,0:04:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.29,0:04:06.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!我也要加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.43,0:04:20.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉娜,放輕鬆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.06,0:04:27.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這個新吉翁紀念性的一夜\n你將在社交界出道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.42,0:04:31.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會祈禱你有個美好的回憶\n是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.12,0:04:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們走吧\n時間差不多到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.63,0:04:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(莉娜\n今晚我一定要把你救出來)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.44,0:04:52.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度.桑達,出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.21,0:04:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度!\n波蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.07,0:05:02.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要,我要跟捷度一起走\n波蕾,你太任性了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.54,0:05:06.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度需要我跟在他身邊的\n不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.29,0:05:19.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是沙比女皇殿下?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.84,0:05:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一直以為是假冒者\n不會錯的,長相太像了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.41,0:05:30.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這位是新吉翁的總帥\n美莉芭.沙比女皇殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.42,0:05:34.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,女皇殿下\n在遠離地球的亞古捷斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.95,0:05:41.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,日夜為了地球與宇宙殖民地的\n友好和平及繁榮而祈禱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.20,0:05:46.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在今天這個好日子\n在巴卡魯這地方能夠留下新吉翁的足跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.49,0:05:49.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,女皇殿下感到無比高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.55,0:05:54.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,承蒙各位參加這場盛大\n在哈曼身為女皇殿下的監護人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.62,0:06:00.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要代替女皇殿下對\n地球聯邦政府的相關人員由衷的答禮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.34,0:06:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你馬上就會習慣的,別忘記保持笑容\n是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.29,0:06:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殿下的邀請是在下無比的光榮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.62,0:06:43.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉娜,仔細看好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.03,0:06:46.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些都是地球聯邦的大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.04,0:06:51.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們是仰賴強者鼻息之外\n沒別的生存方式的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.83,0:06:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(地球聯邦...\n過去不是想打倒沙比家的大人嗎?)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.03,0:07:11.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(那是什麼?大家都在說謊)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.16,0:07:15.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(這裏沒有人是真心的在笑)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.03,0:07:19.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(這扭曲感是什麼?這就是大人嗎?\n這些人究竟怎麼回事?)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.15,0:07:21.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉娜!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.78,0:07:29.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別亂碰,那個不是玩具阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.94,0:07:32.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要攻擊\n還不行阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.49,0:07:35.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在就攻擊\n現在太早了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.35,0:07:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不能因為捷度丟下你就亂來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.88,0:07:39.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.11,0:07:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.00,0:07:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我活著不是為了\n成為這樣的大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.58,0:07:52.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.13,0:07:59.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莫迪,你在幹什麼?\n現在攻擊太早了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.13,0:08:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是波蕾自己開炮的\n我只發了一炮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.79,0:08:04.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要打就瞄準點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.73,0:08:08.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,擊中迎賓館的話\n捷度會打你屁股啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.77,0:08:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我討厭被打屁股
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.04,0:08:17.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你去調查一下!\n是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.93,0:08:21.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你留在這裏,什麼都別擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.84,0:08:24.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(哥哥...)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.86,0:08:53.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位請冷靜,這是慶祝儀式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.53,0:08:59.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位還不相信新吉翁的實力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.68,0:09:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們才會利用卡巴拉的部隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.20,0:09:07.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請各為認清新吉翁展現的實力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.07,0:09:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這只是一場儀式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.79,0:09:19.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈曼大人,美莉芭殿下呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.16,0:09:23.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏交給你了\n是  拜託了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.05,0:09:26.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們走吧,美莉芭殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.33,0:09:30.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(哥哥...)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.94,0:09:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉娜,你等著吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.43,0:09:50.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝,露卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.94,0:10:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在做什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.19,0:10:11.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可疑的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.52,0:10:16.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別開槍,有MS降下來\n我是來通風報信的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.44,0:10:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?在哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.53,0:10:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那邊,那邊\n去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.06,0:10:29.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(怎麼辦?\n只好爬上去了)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.98,0:10:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露卡...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.38,0:10:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.89,0:10:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.65,0:10:55.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幹的好,露卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.46,0:11:01.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉娜...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.96,0:11:15.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(哥哥...)\n你們可以放心,只要我們認真的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.32,0:11:23.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連木星的黑流母線船隻\n都能輕易俘虜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.11,0:11:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真可怕\n你年紀輕輕,卻這麼血氣方剛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.53,0:11:31.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看起來挺可靠的\n真是長江後浪推前浪阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.57,0:11:34.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古利明,我不太舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.19,0:11:37.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到房間休息吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.35,0:11:42.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒事的我可以獨自回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.10,0:11:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不虧是新吉翁的人\n這麼小卻有淑女的氣魄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.09,0:11:52.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你的讚美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.12,0:12:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(一定在附近...不會錯的,哥哥)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.33,0:12:23.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(這個感覺是...)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.19,0:12:26.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈曼大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.52,0:12:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,美莉芭殿下交給你了\n是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.57,0:12:39.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度.桑達,我對你很失望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.14,0:12:41.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想不到你是個不成熟的小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.94,0:12:45.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很遺憾,把你的派對搞砸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.95,0:12:47.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不准動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.38,0:12:49.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不瞭解嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.35,0:12:54.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來這派對向我們新吉翁搖尾的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.14,0:12:56.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才是地球腐敗的根源
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.83,0:13:00.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但那不表示你是正義的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.07,0:13:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在小流星地帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.20,0:13:08.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,注視令人發毛的黑暗又冰冷的宇宙\n活了好幾年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.41,0:13:12.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那期間\n地球愚蠢的人們做了什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.75,0:13:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,過度重建地球\n不顧地球的環境污染
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.61,0:13:22.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還擴大污染,這是不可原諒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.18,0:13:31.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟你在一起\n我就會忍不住說出真話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.99,0:13:33.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真不可思議
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.58,0:13:37.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算這樣\n我也不會當你的手下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.24,0:13:42.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道\n你確實有新人類的素質
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.73,0:13:46.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是你不太瞭解時代潮流了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.23,0:13:49.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一直依賴直覺做事\n小心有一天招來自滅阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.69,0:13:53.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我才不管新人類還不新人類\n我來救莉娜的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.99,0:14:00.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到這時候你還感情用事\n剛開始時還讓我抱有期望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.52,0:14:05.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最後再背叛我\n捷度,桑達,你也一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.11,0:14:12.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哥哥\n莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.96,0:14:14.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.40,0:14:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此,太天真了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.99,0:14:25.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古利明握有控制你的王牌\n卻沒有使用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.25,0:14:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如今那王牌不需要了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.78,0:14:30.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼能..\n讓開,莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.08,0:14:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行,這次換我救哥哥\n莉娜,這場戰爭...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.82,0:14:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很討厭你們這樣溫馨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.68,0:14:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剩下的到天國在上演吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.72,0:14:57.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.72,0:15:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉娜,振作一點,莉娜...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.25,0:15:13.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哥哥...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.64,0:15:28.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.98,0:15:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這感覺...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.46,0:15:36.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼一回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.39,0:15:43.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?\n捷度哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.48,0:15:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈...曼...\n別過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.96,0:16:02.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(什麼?這纏住肌膚的不快感是什麼..)\n失陪一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.95,0:16:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他怎麼了?\n哈曼和美莉芭走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.85,0:16:13.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快逃,這裏很危險阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.34,0:16:17.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別...別過來,別靠近我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.16,0:16:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不...不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.76,0:16:34.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.62,0:16:44.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈曼大人\n讓開!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.22,0:16:49.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈曼大人,你怎麼了\n哈曼大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.41,0:17:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然能對夠對我施以這麼大的壓力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.00,0:17:04.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度.桑達那個人太危險了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.56,0:17:11.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哥哥,放我下來\n不行,你別動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.39,0:17:15.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次換我救出哥哥,所以...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.69,0:17:18.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼不讓我們走?\n你們新吉翁想殺死我們嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.25,0:17:22.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請回去,外面太危險了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.41,0:17:24.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是哈曼大人的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.51,0:17:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要我們待在裏面等轟炸嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.66,0:17:31.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有地球聯邦的各位在\n卡巴拉是不會發動攻擊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.74,0:17:33.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.52,0:17:38.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奉古利明命令要與這個少年回沙達朗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.03,0:17:39.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放我們通行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.28,0:17:41.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼只有你可以出去?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.43,0:17:44.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新吉翁的人算什麼?\n我們...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.26,0:17:50.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住口,你們為何來到派對?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.45,0:17:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有覺悟把地球命運賭在新吉翁上面的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.57,0:17:57.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就應該跟隨我們到最後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.45,0:18:02.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不想成為叛徒的話\n就回去派對會場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.22,0:18:05.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我代美莉芭.沙比殿下命令你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.44,0:18:08.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉娜...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.87,0:18:13.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝擬,莉娜小姐\n我太感動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.79,0:18:18.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連你這麼小的女孩\n都能說出大道理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.06,0:18:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我覺得參加新吉翁陣營\n果然沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.60,0:18:24.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辛苦你了\n是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.95,0:18:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不嫌棄的話\n讓我保護你回沙達朗吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.53,0:18:34.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,保護這裏是你們的使命\n是,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.59,0:18:38.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(莉娜到哪去了?)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.30,0:18:42.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉娜,了不起\n我對你另眼相看了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.94,0:18:45.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是古利明教育得當
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.11,0:18:47.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還痛嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.51,0:18:52.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒問題的,我說了這麼多謊話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.37,0:18:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真是討人厭的女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.11,0:19:00.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣我是無法上天國的\n別說傻話了,很快就能見到艾莉他們,加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.44,0:19:09.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉娜真的跟那個少年一起走了\n是,他說是古利明大人的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.42,0:19:10.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我才沒有命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.00,0:19:16.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.21,0:19:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰?誰在那裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.40,0:19:29.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人受傷了,讓我們過\n讓我們過去,拜託你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.03,0:19:31.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣下去我妹妹會死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.86,0:19:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.37,0:19:45.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是敵人援軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.27,0:19:53.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.23,0:19:59.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡的捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.44,0:20:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉娜是我辛苦教育出來的\n怎麼能讓你隨便帶走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.99,0:20:12.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,振作點,莉娜\n我馬上帶你去療傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.05,0:20:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行,必須變成ZZ高達\n伊萊,來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.59,0:20:33.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是捷度的訊號\n伊萊,去支援他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.89,0:20:36.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了\n露卡,前面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.97,0:20:41.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會總是讓你們得逞的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.21,0:20:46.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伊萊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.14,0:20:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古利明!\n什麼?是露卡嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.22,0:20:59.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你太纏人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.36,0:21:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉娜,振作點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.00,0:21:09.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伊萊在幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.41,0:21:12.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攻擊那裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.65,0:21:16.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,疑?我什麼也看不見\n捷度有危險了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.32,0:21:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.18,0:21:24.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉娜!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.60,0:21:29.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,振作一點\n不行,得馬上看醫生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.55,0:21:31.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在不是戰鬥的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.64,0:21:39.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發射信號彈了,趕快撤退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.81,0:21:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人數目一直增加\n我沒辦法脫身阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.84,0:21:53.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是援軍嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.98,0:21:58.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加油阿,莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.29,0:22:00.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.05,0:22:07.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住手!\n現在不是戰鬥的時候阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.91,0:22:18.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行,控制失靈了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.84,0:22:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定要支持下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.30,0:22:49.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成百 成萬 上億的繁星啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.49,0:22:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何只是閃耀而已 展示你言語的能力吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.55,0:23:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在我也能不回頭地 讓心靈出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.70,0:23:12.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若能把多如繁星的生命儲存的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.65,0:23:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把整個銀河也化作光芒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.35,0:23:28.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,化作緊握在掌心的 生命的重量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.32,0:23:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我仍未能看見宇宙的路標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.22,0:23:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,手掌觸摸著一千萬年的光芒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.66,0:23:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我把受傷的莉娜交給了波蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.31,0:23:53.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我卻沒有發現兩人間微妙的裂痕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.66,0:23:56.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在某處大鬧的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.16,0:24:02.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古利明的部下的MS墜向了二人所在的建築物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.96,0:24:06.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下集 高達ZZ 莉娜的血 下集
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.98,0:24:10.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真是丟臉的NEWTYPE！

